      <MissionDesc>THE MISSION AT NATES PLACE, A WELLNESS AND RECOVERY CENTER, IS TO DELIVER TARGETED PROGRAMS, HEALTHY REPLACEMENT ACTIVITIES, AND 1:1 PEER SUPPORT RECOVERY COACHING TO TEENS AND YOUNG ADULTS (AGES 13-25), WHO ARE AT RISK OF SUBSTANCE ABUSE AND/OR MENTAL HEALTH DISORDERS, OR STRIVING TO ATTAIN AND MAINTAIN SOBRIETY AND MENTAL HEALTH IN A SAFE, HEALTHY MANNER. NATE'S PLACE, A WELLNESS AND RECOVERY CENTER FILLS A GAP IN SERVICES FOR UNDERSERVED,UNINSURED AND LOW INCOME INDIVIDUALS. WE PROVIDE THE FOLLOWING SERVICES, FREE OF CHARGE, WITH FREE TRANSPORTATION: 1. 1:1 PEER SUPPORT RECOVERY COACHING FOR EVERY PARTICIPANT 2. 20+ HEALTHY RECREATIONAL ACTIVITIES 3. 13 GROUPS THAT PROVIDE COUNSELING, EDUCATION AND SUPPORT 4. BI-MONTHLY COMMUNITY EDUCATION TALKS ON MENTAL HEALTH AND SUBSTANCE USE 5. TEEN INTERVENE PREVENTION GROUPS IN 13 SCHOOLS ACROSS VENTURA COUNTY</MissionDesc>
